{"tid":864511,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"為中國設立再教育營辯護    新疆主席：當地邪氣下降","createTime":"2018-10-16T09:07:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-16T11:07:12.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8036838cf309456732a8f6df70f34d6c7340c2f3","tid":864511,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T09:07:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/CdW9i1Jd73g7iRMAjkKzNg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzY4O2g9NTEyO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/afp/int0008b.181016140502.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FCdW9i1Jd73g7iRMAjkKzNg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzY4O2g9NTEyO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fafp%2Fint0008b.181016140502.jpg&h=7614d621&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">環球時報昨晚發出社評強調，新疆透過加 強治理避免世界其他地方上演的各種極端情況，應被視 為「化解高風險局勢的難得正面範例」</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（法新社北京16日電） 中國在新疆設立「職業技能 教育培訓中心」引發西方國家批評後，新疆自治區主席 雪克來提&bull;扎克爾出面稱，「新疆已連續21個月未發生 暴力恐怖案件」。<br />\n<br />\n雪克來提&bull;扎克爾罕見接受新華社專訪，說明中共 的「治疆方略」，強調當前新疆呈現出大局穩定、形勢 可控、趨勢向好的態勢。 他說，新疆依法展開職業技能教育培訓工作，目的 就是要從根本上消除滋生恐怖主義、宗教極端主義的環 境和土壤，將暴恐活動消除在未發之前。 <br />\n<br />\n雪克來提&bull;扎克爾稱，在展開職業技能教育培訓工 作的影響下，新疆社會環境發生明顯變化，「正氣上升 ，邪氣下降」，宗教極端思想傳播受到自覺抵制，反恐 維穩和去極端化工作的群眾基礎更加牢固，「各族群眾 對未來美好生活充滿希望」。 他聲稱，實踐證明，展開職業技能教育培訓工作符 合目前新疆反恐維穩和去極端化工作實際，是新疆探索 消除滋生恐怖主義、極端主義環境和土壤，預防暴力恐 怖犯罪的有效舉措。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%BE%AF%E8%AD%B7%E5%86%8D%E6%95%99%E8%82%B2%E7%87%9F-%E6%96%B0%E7%96%86%E4%B8%BB%E5%B8%AD-%E7%95%B6%E5%9C%B0%E9%82%AA%E6%B0%A3%E4%B8%8B%E9%99%8D-060502702.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E8%25BE%25AF%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E5%2586%258D%25E6%2595%2599%25E8%2582%25B2%25E7%2587%259F-%25E6%2596%25B0%25E7%2596%2586%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E5%25B8%25AD-%25E7%2595%25B6%25E5%259C%25B0%25E9%2582%25AA%25E6%25B0%25A3%25E4%25B8%258B%25E9%2599%258D-060502702.html&d=19R18GhNToue5Ck1nXThu8mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=b125cfe6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%BE%AF%E8%AD%B7%E5%86%8D%E6%95%99%E8%82%B2%E7%87%9F-%E6%96%B0%E7%96%86%E4%B8%BB%E5%B8%AD-%E7%95%B6%E5%9C%B0%E9%82%AA%E6%B0%A3%E4%B8%8B%E9%99%8D-060502702.html</a>"},{"pid":"35c9a33a360955eafac13bf40776fbe217b4b163","tid":864511,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T09:39:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed24d1df170e9e1a80c1dda9d5f3ee487133a6b4","tid":864511,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T11:05:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/41.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88d943ed4b3125699135fb396a2ce4517d4d5e43","tid":864511,"uid":121095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T11:07:12.000Z","msg":"點解有種香港政府官員講野既feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}